column2: SELECT   p.ra,p.dec,p.g,p.r,  s.z, s.snMedian_r,  s.velDisp,  s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid,  s.chunk, s.boss_target1, INTO BOSS_sample_sn7_DR1# FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN stellarMassPassivePort AS stM ON s.specObjID = stM.specObjID WHERE   s.z BETWEEN # AND #  AND  s.survey = &&&  AND  s.class = &&&  AND  s.snMedian_r > #  AND   s.velDIsp BETWEEN # AND #  AND  s.zWARNING = #
